These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, daisy
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, prince
1. the siglo-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the prince-smoker is not the person who growsdaisy##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | daisy   | rose  |
| Sport   | siglo | prince |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, ship
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, photography
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is not the person driving the ship##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | bus | ship      |
| Pet    | hiking  | photography |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
House: futuristic, cape-cod
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, mexican
1. the cape-cod house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
2. the colombian is not the futuristic house##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |
| Food    | cape-cod  | futuristic    |
| Sport   | colombian | mexican |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-4::.
City: boston, berlin
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, brazilian
1. the person traveling to berlin is not the russian##6
2. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to boston##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2      |
| Food   | boston  | berlin |
| Pet    | russian | brazilian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-5::.
